{"tid":1625163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求用一分鐘睇左佢","createTime":"2019-10-05T06:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:12:49.000Z","uid":185303,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c973a718d08fafcf57edd0890b729779373caf2d","tid":1625163,"uid":185303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:03:27.000Z","msg":"搞鋪頭係 <br />\n成本大 俾人拉 俾人屌 影響民居 有人偷竊 變暴徒<br />\n但無效益 同五大訴求有關係？ <br />\n<br />\n手足們真係要小心三思 宜家係講緊成個社會既存亡 唔係藍黃杯葛行動咁簡單 唔岩聽都要講<br />\n<br />\n我地輸唔起香港既前途<br />\n<br />\n政權制度係我地既敵人啊<br />\n係搞就要搞得岩搞得好<br />\n<br />\n議員辦事處 政府部門 大把啦<br />\n<br />\n藍鋪咪由佢罷食自己收皮摺左<br />\n<br />\n唔好嬲到失曬焦 俾支共利用做新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8749ca6a2f676ef98ec3ebe600df592fbfc289f","tid":1625163,"uid":304456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:12:07.000Z","msg":"仲要做裝修班靚仔好細個，較難入到係黑警做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4c71b862dff77cb2b3b36bd2bdc13b00852d835","tid":1625163,"uid":304456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T06:12:49.000Z","msg":"勉強話係王祖藍做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}